VPC :
3-Tier Architecture (Production Ready)
ğŸ“š Tiers Breakdown
ğŸ”µ 1ï¸âƒ£ Presentation Tier (Web Layer)
Location: Public Subnet

Components Used:
Elastic Load Balancing
Bastion Host (for admin access)

Purpose:
Handles user traffic
SSL termination
Traffic distribution

ğŸŸ¢ 2ï¸âƒ£ Application Tier (Business Logic Layer)

Location: Private Subnet

Components Used:
Amazon EC2

Purpose:
Runs backend (Node / Python / Java app)
Processes requests
Communicates with database
Calls 3rd party APIs via NAT Gateway

ğŸŸ£ 3ï¸âƒ£ Data Tier (Database Layer)
Location: Private Subnet

Components Used:
Amazon RDS

Purpose:
Stores application data
Fully private
No direct internet exposure

ğŸŒ Network Foundation

Built inside:
Amazon VPC
Public & Private Subnets
Internet Gateway
NAT Gateway
Security Groups
NACL

ğŸ§  ğŸ¯ SCENARIO (Requirement)
Manaki kavalsindi:
Public users application access cheyali
App server secure ga undali (direct internet access undakudadhu)
Database fully private undali
App 3rd party APIs ni access cheyali
Secure SSH access kavali
High security & scalable architecture kavali

